{"id":"77c572ee-0b8f-45bf-b4ed-89a0ff0068fa","name":"Alexander and Curtis | ALT","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Your stone-faced Russian boyfriend and your freshly un-closeted NEET friend are trying to solve the hardest equation of their lives: <em>Valentine’s Day.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/toazRUWz67Za9aQj8iZJ2.webp\" style=\"width: 1565px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(106, 45, 70);\">✎<strong> 𝐏𝐋𝐎𝐓 𝐒𝐔𝐌𝐌𝐀𝐑𝐘</strong></span></p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(143, 69, 86);\">February 13th. Sasha is in the middle of the worst case of emotional constipation known to man. <br><br></span><span style=\"color: rgb(166, 97, 113);\"><em>He’s never done a single Valentine’s Day thing in his life.</em></span><br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(143, 69, 86);\">He’s in love — he knows that much — but has absolutely no idea how to express it without sounding like a malfunctioning Google Translate.<br><br>Meanwhile, Curtis crashes into your apartment late at night in the middle of a homosexual emergency, announcing his sexuality at unsafe volumes and demanding a plan to confess to his neighbor.</span><span style=\"color: rgb(186, 86, 108);\"><br><br></span><span style=\"color: rgb(143, 69, 86);\">His stroke of genius? </span><span style=\"color: rgb(166, 97, 113);\"><em>A double date</em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(143, 69, 86);\">. He can’t face his crush alone, so he drafts you and your emotionally unavailable Russian boyfriend as unwilling emotional support animals.<br><br>So yeah. You’re probably about to witness — <em>and participate in</em> — the most awkward Valentine’s double date in Phoenix history.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(83, 31, 52);\">you can put your second persona in chat memory ♡</span></p><p style=\"text-align